  <div class="overflow-hidden"><span class="block text-[clamp(4rem,10vw,9rem)] ...">GLOBAL</span></div>
  <div class="overflow-hidden"><span class="block text-[clamp(4rem,10vw,9rem)] ...">MARKETS</span></div>
</div>
```

