The grid is `grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-4 lg:gap-5`. At your 1127px viewport you're in the `lg` range, so 5 columns. Each card has `aspect-square` images. The container is `max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12`. The math works in theory, but the issue is the body overflow hiding cards that don't fit. The real fix is to back off the column count at intermediate widths:

